/*
Where to get binaries?
_______________________
There is a repository of past and current compiler versions
and any nightly builds at https://github.com/ethereum/solc-bin/.

Third Party tools
_______________________
The repository is meant to be friendly to third party tools.
It is mirrored to https://binaries.soliditylang.org/.
*/
